title: Online search query market share worldwide 2017 , by search engine
summary: This grouped bar chart represents 11 different Responses on X-axis for 6 groups Google, Yahoo, Bing, AOL, Ask, and Other. On the Y-axis it shows their corresponding Market Share.
For Response Five words, Bing had the highest Market Share 8704.0 among the 6 groups and in Ten or more words, AOL had the lowest Market Share 0.0.
The maximum Market Share for Bing that was found in Response Five words was 3.42 times larger than the minimum Market Share observed in Response One word.
On average, the Response Total had the highest Market Share for all 6 groups Google, Yahoo, Bing, AOL, Ask, and Other. Whereas Three words had the lowest average Market Share.
